Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.31,0:01:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Membiarkan Tuan Arthur terserang pilek\Nadalah dosa besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sisa energi kehidupan dikonfirmasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.71,0:01:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hukuman mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada kata-kata terakhir?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.40,0:01:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku tak menyesal dalam hidup ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, pelayan pribadi\Ndari sang Pewaris, Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.35,0:02:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Identitas aslinya adalah pelayan robot\Nyang dikembangkan konglomerat Zetes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.11,0:02:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu mustahil!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.98,0:02:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sebenarnya manusia\Nyang menyamar sebagai robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.13,0:02:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Andai pria itu tak menemukan masa laluku...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.99,0:02:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masa lalu Marie diketahui seseorang, Noah,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}seorang pembunuh bawahan Maynard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.92,0:02:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Bagaimana bisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua catatan tentangmu\Nseharusnya sudah dihapus.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.72,0:02:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, sekarang, yang terpenting\Nadalah merawat Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Agar Tuan Arthur pulih,\Naku akan melakukan apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kupegang janjimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku punya sesuatu untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini yang dipakai Tuan Muda...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudku, yang dimanfaatkan ayah Tuan Muda\Nsaat terkena pilek.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:02:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini set perawat yang konon\Nbisa menyembuhkan semua penyakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, aku tak yakin apa isinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.04,0:03:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak boleh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur, Anda tak boleh belajar.\NBerbaringlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.06,0:03:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan halangi aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku punya tugas OSIS hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus mengadakan\Npesta hari jadi sekolah nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, dengan kondisi Anda...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah itu tugas OSIS\Natau mengadakan acara, mereka memilihku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan kata lain,\Nada orang yang tidak terpilih.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengerti betapa besar\Npenyesalan membebani hati mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini juga masalah yang harus kuhadapi\Nsebagai pewaris Zetes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lupa mengambil dokumennya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang saatnya menggunakannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa sudah waktunya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkinkah ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seharusnya itu di sekitar sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak mengerti,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:05:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi konon pakaian ini sangat ampuh\Nsaat pria Zetes terserang pilek.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur, tolong berbaring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bermimpi Marie mendorongku\Ndengan pakaian perawat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku menjadi orang mesum?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, ini bukan imajinasiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin itu hanya mode perawat Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jelas bukan orang mesum.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, aku akan tenang dan berbaring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,\Naku akan mengukur suhu tubuh Anda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong jangan bergerak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.59,0:05:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf sebelumnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bukankah itu cara manusia\Nsaling mengukur suhu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga, aku harus cari alasan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.53,0:06:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, saya...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Punya sensor suhu tubuh di dahi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mudah tertipu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suhu tubuh Anda sangat tinggi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar saya seka keringat Anda.\NTolong lepaskan bajunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jernihkan pikiran...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau boleh, punggungnya juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biasanya aku tak membiarkan orang\Nmelihat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keseharianku selalu dekat dengan kematian.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:07:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah sering terluka sejak kecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luka dalam di punggungku ini\Nkonon mengikutiku seumur hidup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai sekarang,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}saya tak akan membiarkan siapa pun\Nmenyakiti Tuan Arthur lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya akan melindungi Anda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.43,0:07:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semoga hanya aku yang melihat\Nsisi rentan Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, ini sungguh mimpi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurut informasi,\NArthur tampaknya dalam kondisi kritis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, target hampir mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu cosplay perawat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang benar saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang kamu lakukan?\NPadahal ada kesempatan menghabisinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.18,0:08:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ornamen keluarga Zetes memang hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.85,0:08:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini berat dan keras sehingga\Ncocok untuk menghantam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bodoh, mereka hanya umpan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kupakai kesempatan ini...\NMustahil!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.74,0:08:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf atas keributan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang sudah tenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beristirahatlah, Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jadi tenang\Nsaat tidak merasa sendirian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebelum Marie, tak ada yang bisa membuatku\Nmenunjukkan sisi rentanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya aku terus berpura-pura kuat,\Nmenunjukkan versi palsu diriku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski aku paling benci kebohongan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:09:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur, aku sedang membohongimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, lebih dari rasa bersalah ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku hanya mau bersama orang ini selamanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perasaan ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Noah, kamu di sana?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.30,0:09:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu butuh sesuatu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.67,0:09:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini, Tuan Maynard?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu selalu mendekatiku seperti ini,\Nkarena itu aku memegangnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menjauh dariku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,\Nkamu sudah mendapatkan benda itu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksud Anda ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ponsel Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.07,0:09:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah menghapus videonya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang, kita bisa\Nmenghabisi Arthur tanpa ragu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.58,0:09:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, tangkap dia hidup-hidup.\NAku akan menghabisinya sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini adalah\NPesta Hari Jadi SMA Carmia,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sekolah bergengsi tempat Arthur belajar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pesta yang dihadiri oleh orang kaya\Ndan berkuasa di kota ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Setiap tahun, mereka harus datang\N- Berkat partisipasi kalian,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.47,0:10:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- dengan memakai kostum.\N- sekolah kita bisa lebih berkembang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suatu kehormatan bagiku
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Syukurlah.\N- untuk menyambut kalian di pesta ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tuan Arthur tampak jauh lebih baik.\N- Selamat menikmati.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, apa kamu lelah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.55,0:10:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, mungkin agak aneh\Nkalau bertanya seperti itu pada robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Banyak sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.05,0:10:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap kamu juga bisa menikmati pestanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat pakaian ini, semua orang di kelas\Nbilang aku tampak tampan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie berpakaian sebagai pelayan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu manis sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang punya sesuatu untuk memukulnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih baik lagi kalau ujungnya tajam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senator yang kami temui\Ndi pesta sebelumnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.00,0:11:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lama tak bertemu.\NTerima kasih untuk tempo hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, aku akan bicara dengan Senator.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bosan sekali.\NAku akan mencari makanan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini gawat.\NAku harus menyingkirkan Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Noah,\Nkamu mengambil terlalu banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Tak boleh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku salah orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku berpakaian seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Noah memberikan ini padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kecuali aku,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- lihat, tak ada yang punya kostum.\N- Vam-vam-vam,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:12:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Noah sangat membantu.\N- vampir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menipuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Roy, tolong beri tahu aku\Nlokasi GPS Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, ikuti arahanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur, hati-hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.26,0:12:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika ada hal penting yang mau kamu bahas,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}datanglah ke rumahku nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.81,0:12:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku melakukan ini demi keluargaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu, menggunakan nyawa anggota keluarga\Nadalah cara paling efektif.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, aku tak mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu masih bisa bergerak.\NGigih sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa di sana?\NDi mana kamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kesadaranmu memudar?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu diberi obat penenang khusus
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang melemahkan\Nsaraf penglihatan dan pendengaranmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:13:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dalam kondisi ini, mayoritas orang\Nakan memohon ampun dengan menyedihkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak menduga kamu bisa melawannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.69,0:13:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski terlihat kuat,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kurasa kamu tak bisa menahan\Nsuntikan kedua.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga, padahal suntikan ini untuk Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan memanfaatkanmu sebagai umpan\Nuntuk memancing Marie ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, jauh di dalam ruangan di ujung,\Nada ruangan lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sinyal GPS berasal dari dalam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, selain itu, Tuan Roy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.61,0:13:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tempat ini...\NApa ini ruangan tak terpakai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jauh di dalam ruangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur, aku akan menyelamatkanmu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.48,0:13:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu datang cepat sekali.\NLuar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan saat pisau ditusukkan\Nke arah lehermu, kamu tak tersentak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sesuai dugaan, Marie memang\Nlebih baik daripada semua orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitukah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu meleset lagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pada akhirnya,\Naku tak pernah mengalahkanmu sekali pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.33,0:14:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya aku melatih ulang diriku\Nuntuk hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku juga akan serius.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, kamu sungguh hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai sekarang, aku tak pernah berpikir\Nuntuk berpasangan dengan siapa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, jika bersamamu, aku merasa
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan senang melakukan pembunuhan kontrak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa yang mau melakukan\Npekerjaan seperti itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:15:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pelayan Tuan Arthur!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sangat menyebalkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.80,0:15:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lebih mengenalmu daripada Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bahkan bilang mencintaimu apa adanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat membutuhkanmu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, kamu akan lebih bahagia bersamaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayolah, katakan aku benar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tangan kanannya lebih lemah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.35,0:15:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang kesempatanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial, karena pistol setrum\Nyang waktu itu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.66,0:16:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gelap sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.04,0:16:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu pikir bisa kabur dengan cara ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayang sekali.\NMataku sudah terbiasa dengan kegelapan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nah, kemarilah, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bukan Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagus, Marie-2.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu robot pelayan\Nyang lebih hebat daripada aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.38,0:16:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuserahkan sisanya padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia lemah, tapi tak ada luka luar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur aman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, Marie-2.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana dia?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga! Zombi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana Marie-2?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.41,0:17:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sungguh minta maaf...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.63,0:17:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kuduga, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu mencintai Arthur, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, tidakkah kamu mengerti?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.49,0:17:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur hanya mencintai\Nrobot bernama Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan dirimu yang sebenarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin tahu bagaimana reaksi Arthur\Nsaat dia tahu kamu manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu harus merelakan cinta seperti itu\Nsecepat mungkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, kamu bukan tipe orang\Nyang dicintai oleh siapa pun, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama ini, kamu selalu dibenci dan dijauhi\Noleh semua orang di sekitarmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.41,0:18:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitulah kamu hidup sampai sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai sekarang,\Nkamu akan terus hidup sendirian.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.21,0:18:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu yang paling cocok untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jalanilah hidup tanpa orang mencintaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.52,0:18:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan dengarkan dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.44,0:18:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana bisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.36,0:18:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Obat sebanyak itu\Nseharusnya melumpuhkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang yang menyakiti Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.20,0:18:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana kamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.91,0:18:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keluar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski hampir tidak sadarkan diri,\Nkamu masih memikirkanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku seperti boneka tanpa ekspresi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga masih punya hati!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.05,0:19:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa pun kata orang,\Naku akan tetap di sisinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur, bertahanlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tidak sadar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Adalah orang yang bisa melindungi\Norang lain sepertiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia adalah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang yang menyelamatkan hatiku,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}orang yang membuatku merasakan\Nindahnya jatuh cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.05,0:19:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, dia juga yang paling kucintai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mencintai Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Noah tidak datang hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia pilek?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Membosankan sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.11,0:20:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu wajar karena aku memberinya\Nluka yang fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pria itu tak akan lagi datang ke sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia datang!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tak perlu begitu mewaspadaiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.15,0:20:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku terluka parah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa melakukan pembunuhan\Nuntuk sementara.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,\Nsetelah menyadari tentang perasaanmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.77,0:20:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa kamu bisa mempertahankannya\Nbersama Arthur?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.64,0:20:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cinta yang dibangun di atas kebohongan ini\Npasti akan berakhir dengan tragedi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.24,0:20:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya,\Nkalau mau lari dari kebohongan itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.32,0:20:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}datanglah padaku kapan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:21:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bukan urusanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hai, selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.84,0:21:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejujurnya, aku terjatuh telentang\Ndi pesta kemarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya kamu diserang\Ndan cukup menderita.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap pelakunya segera tertangkap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah kenapa, saat diserang kemarin,\Naku mendengar suaramu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu berkhayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia jatuh, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.95,0:21:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak tahu dia bisa seceroboh itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.94,0:21:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur, sepertinya hari ini\Nsuasana hati Anda sedang baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.57,0:21:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.85,0:21:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bermimpi semalam\Nsaat tidak sadarkan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.04,0:21:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu mimpi yang indah\Nhingga aku berharap itu bisa terwujud.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.35,0:21:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie akhirnya mengatakan\Nperasaannya yang sebenarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semoga suatu hari nanti, Arthur juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.79,0:23:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Marie-2,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.97,0:23:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}robot pelayan kedua\Nyang melayani Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.60,0:23:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Demi cinta dan keadilan,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.98,0:23:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan melakukan yang terbaik!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.99,0:23:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cinta... Perasaan cintaku...